    "🌽🍓 IT'S BACK! The Oshkosh Farmers Market returns THIS SATURDAY! 🎉 Join us on the 400 & 500 blocks of N. Main St. and the 100 block of Church Ave. this Saturday, May 30 from 8 a.m. – 12:30 p.m. for Opening Day of one of the BEST farmers markets in the country! Explore 165+ vendors featuring fresh seasonal produce, local meats and poultry, artisan breads, handmade crafts, ready-to-eat foods, live music, and so much more. Rain or shine — see you there every Saturday through October 31! 🌿☀️ 📍 Downtown Oshkosh, N. Main St. 🕗 Saturdays | 8 a.m. – 12:30 p.m. 🔗 https://bit.ly/4nYo4mE",
